This template adds the podman to the image.

Podman is a daemonless container engine for developing,
managing, and running OCI Containers on your Linux System.
Containers can either be run as root or in rootless mode.
Simply put: alias docker=podman.

Detail description can be found in:
https://podman.io

To use the template, add "--templates feature/podman" as a setup
option.

#@TYPE: Wrtemplate
#@NAME: podman
#@DESCRIPTION: install podman into image

